{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_12_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "もう九月かぁ……\n夏休みは終わったけど、まだまだ暑いよね",
      "startTime": 3.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.4229252974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "こんな暑い日はばしゃーんって水に飛び込みたくなるよ\n冷たくて気持ちいいだろうな～",
      "startTime": 12.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0026986916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "夏の涼み方までアクティブなのは芽衣らしいな\n芽衣は暑さで気が滅入ったりしないのか？",
      "startTime": 19.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、照りつける太陽を見たら\n「夏だー！」って感じで元気がわいてくるかな？",
      "startTime": 26.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9085493565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あと、桜が咲いてるのを見たら\n「春だー！」って元気になるし",
      "startTime": 33.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "落ち葉を見たら「秋だー！」って元気になるし\n雪を見たら「冬だー！」って元気になるよね！",
      "startTime": 39.9666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.474987364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "年中元気で羨ましいよ\n芽衣は夏バテなんてしなさそうだな",
      "startTime": 47.2333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.2338306746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね～。今年は海で合宿したり、ミクちゃんの\nライブに出演したり、すっごく充実してたでしょ？",
      "startTime": 54.7333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで毎日楽しくて\n夏の疲れも全部吹き飛んじゃった",
      "startTime": 60.433335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.643832366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも、この夏でひとつだけ心残りがあるかも……",
      "startTime": 63.643832366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.0042858444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなと海に行った時\n一緒に{user}さんも来てくれたでしょ？",
      "startTime": 71.4000020346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、芽衣は{user}さんと\n全然遊べなかったんだよね",
      "startTime": 76.8000020346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.6859873457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、海ではすずに振り回されて\n芽衣の相手はあまり出来なかったな",
      "startTime": 83.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんと\nもっと水遊びしたかったな～",
      "startTime": 87.033335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.6988236431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ！　プールに行こうよ！\n夏が終わる前に、一緒にプールで遊ぶの！",
      "startTime": 93.833335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.1719981197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われても、仕事が忙しいしな……\nプールに遊びに行く余裕なんてあるかどうか",
      "startTime": 101.3000020346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.6108187996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、月ストでプール関係のお仕事を\n取ってくればいいんだよ！",
      "startTime": 107.333335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達がプールでお仕事をすれば\n付き添いで一緒に来られるでしょ？",
      "startTime": 111.633335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.2846961978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そう都合良く仕事が舞い込むか分からないが……\nそうだな、その時は一緒に夏を満喫させてもらうよ",
      "startTime": 117.9318073275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.2446960452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "やったぁ！　約束だよ？\nプールでのお仕事、早くこないかな～",
      "startTime": 125.733335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 130.8471223198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.9804556532
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.9804556532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ！\nプールで撮影するお仕事が入ったって本当なの！？",
      "startTime": 133.8666687013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.300975625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。ライブでミクと歌った新曲が\n正式にリリースされることに決まってな",
      "startTime": 140.3666687013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "楽曲の雰囲気に合わせて\nプールでMVを撮影することになったんだ",
      "startTime": 145.0000020346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1431978068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "ミクちゃんと一緒に作ったあの曲が\nリリースされることになったの！？",
      "startTime": 150.433335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.7238328458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "そっかぁ……夏を歌った曲だもんね\nMVにプールの映像はぴったりだよ",
      "startTime": 157.4666687013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "新曲のリリース、嬉しいな～\nそれに、プールに行く約束も叶えてくれてありがと～！",
      "startTime": 164.5333475751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.8064976216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "たまたまタイミング良く撮影の話がきただけだから\n俺に礼を言うことじゃないよ",
      "startTime": 172.1333475751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、芽衣との約束を覚えててくれたんだよね？",
      "startTime": 174.3057494958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.3057494958
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それはまぁ……芽衣が喜ぶと思ったから\nスケジュールの調整で多少無理はしたが……",
      "startTime": 182.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
